n. It's not listed as one of our values, but \"Thanks Science!\" is a popular phrase Purple uses for swag and social media. Science isn't expressly stated in our current values; it underlies several of them. As a data analyst, that is attractive. I believe in science, I invest in knowledge."), mdx("h2", null, "How to Start with Why"), mdx("p", null, "I bought ", mdx("a", {
